rComments: Wonderful Teacher! She is really a gem of the midwest. You will work hard, but sooo rewarding!

One of the most amazing voice teachers in the country! Her students sing professionally all over the world, and have won major competitions. Her incredible musicianship and insistence on unmanipulated vocal production make her an invaluable resource for singers, young and old!

One of the greatest voice teachers in the country! Her professional experience as an opera star abroad and in the US is incredible (and helpful!), and her technique, singing with complete reliance on the breath, produces some of the finest young artists in the US today. One of my most important musical instructors of all time!
